easy_install simplejson
easy_install anyjson
easy_install celery
easy_install sqlalchemy # for celery to store data
sudo port install rabbitmq-server

sudo rabbitmq-server -detached 
python2.7 manage.py celeryd --loglevel=DEBUG -E
python2.7 manage.py celerybeat --loglevel=DEBUG
python2.7 manage.py celeryev


database.py tells celery to store tasks in web2py db (incomplete)
views.py exposes APIs. Almost done!